{
  "texts": [
    "It finds application in decision-making processes, future predictions, and problem-solving, eliminating the necessity for explicit programming.",
    "Positioned as a subset of both artificial intelligence and data science, machine learning exemplifies the evolution of intelligent systems capable of independent learning and adaptive problem-solving.",
    "-Deep Learning: It is a subset of machine learning, representing one of the most advanced branches within the realm of artificial intelligence.",
    "This sophisticated approach empowers machines to emulate human learning and cognition, necessitating a complex structure that mirrors the neural networks found in the human brain.",
    "The primary objective of deep learning is to comprehend intricate patterns, even when faced with noise and incomplete details."
  ]
}